\f3\i\b responsible entity
\f0\i0\b0 , for an asset, has the same meaning as in the 
\f2\i Security of Critical Infrastructure Act 2018
\f0\i0 .\

\f3\i\b Secretary
\f0\i0\b0  means the Secretary of the Department.\

\f3\i\b sensitive information
\f0\i0\b0  has the same meaning as in the 
\f2\i Privacy Act 1988
\f0\i0 .\

\f3\i\b sensitive review information
