\f3\i\b significant cyber security incident 
\f0\i0\b0 has the meaning given by section\'a034.
\f3\i\b \
State body
\f0\i0\b0  means:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	a Minister of a State or Territory; or\
	(b)	a Department of State of a State or Territory or a Department of the Public Service of a State or Territory; or\
	(c)	a body (whether incorporated or not) that:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	is established, or continued in existence, for a public purpose by or under a law of a State or Territory; and\
	(ii)	is not an authority of the Crown.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f3\i\b \cf0 supply 
