\f2\i\b0\fs22 \cf0 Responding to notices to produce\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\i0 \cf0 	(1)	An entity is not liable to an action or other proceeding for damages for or in relation to an act done or omitted in good faith in compliance with section\'a049 (Chair may obtain documents from certain entities).\
	(2)	An officer, employee or agent of an entity is not liable to an action for damages for or in relation to an act done or omitted in good faith in connection with an act done or omitted by the entity as mentioned in subsection\'a0(1).\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf0 The Board etc.\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\i0 \cf0 	(3)	A person who is or has been:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	the Chair; or\
	(b)	a standing member of the Board; or\
	(c)	a member of the Expert Panel; or\
	(d)	a member of the staff assisting the Board (as mentioned in section\'a071); or\
	(e)	a consultant assisting the Board (as mentioned in section\'a072); or\
	(f)	a witness appearing in a review;\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 is not liable to an action or other proceeding for damages for or in relation to an act done or omitted in good faith in the performance or purported performance of a function or duty conferred by this Part, or the exercise or purported exercise of a power conferred by this Part.\
