\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs22 \cf0 	(1)	The Chair may issue a certificate stating that a specified person who is, or has been:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	a standing member of the Board; or\
	(b)	a member of the Expert Panel; or\
	(c)	a member of the staff assisting the Board (as mentioned in section\'a071); or\
	(d)	a consultant assisting the Board (as mentioned in section\'a072); or\
	(e)	a witness appearing in a review;\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 is involved, or has been involved, in a review under this Part\'a0into a specified matter.\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(2)	The Secretary may issue a certificate stating that a specified person who is, or has been, the Chair is involved, or has been involved, in a review under this Part\'a0into a specified matter.\
	(3)	If, under subsection\'a0(1) or (2), a certificate is issued in relation to a person and a specified matter, the person:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	is not obliged to comply with a subpoena or similar direction of a federal court or a court of a State or Territory to attend and answer questions relating to the matter; and\
