\f2\i Public Governance, Performance and Accountability Act 2013
\f0\i0  for a reporting period must also include the following:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	the number of each of the following during the period:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	reviews commenced;\
	(ii)	reviews completed;\
	(iii)	reviews discontinued;\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(b)	a brief description of each of those reviews;\
	(c)	the status of any reviews not yet completed at the end of the period;\
	(d)	the reasons for discontinuing any reviews during the period;\
	(e)	the number of times the Minister refused to approve the terms of reference for a review during the period;\
	(f)	the number of members of the Expert Panel during the period;\
