\f1\i0\b\fs24 \cf0 85  How this Act applies in relation to non\uc0\u8209 legal persons\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

\f2\i\b0\fs22 \cf0 How permissions and rights are conferred and exercised\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\i0 \cf0 	(1)	If this Act purports to confer a permission or right on an entity that is not a legal person, the permission or right:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	is conferred on each person who is an accountable person for the entity at the time the permission or right may be exercised; and\
	(b)	may be exercised by:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	any person who is an accountable person for the entity at the time the permission or right may be exercised; or\
	(ii)	any person who is authorised by a person referred to in subparagraph\'a0(i) to exercise the permission or right.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf0 How obligations and duties are imposed and discharged\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\i0 \cf0 	(2)	If this Act purports to impose an obligation or duty on an entity that is not a legal person, the obligation or duty:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	is imposed on each person who is an accountable person for the entity at the time the obligation or duty arises or is in operation; and\
	(b)	may be discharged by:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	any person who is an accountable person for the entity at the time the obligation or duty arises or is in operation; or\
	(ii)	any person who is authorised by a person referred to in subparagraph\'a0(i) to discharge the obligation or duty.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf0 How non\uc0\u8209 legal persons contravene this Act\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\i0 \cf0 	(3)	A provision of this Act (including a civil penalty provision) that is purportedly contravened by an entity that is not a legal person is instead contravened by each accountable person for the entity who:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	did the relevant act or made the relevant omission; or\
	(b)	aided, abetted, counselled or procured the relevant act or omission; or\
	(c)	was in any way knowingly concerned in, or party to, the relevant act or omission.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\ri1933\sb240\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf0 Meaning of 
\f3\b accountable person
\f2\b0 \
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\i0 \cf0 	(4)	For the purposes of this section, a person is an 
\f3\i\b accountable person 
\f0\i0\b0 for an entity at a particular time if:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	in the case of a partnership in which one or more of the partners is an individual\'97the individual is a partner in the partnership at that time; or\
	(b)	in the case of a partnership in which one or more of the partners is a body corporate\'97the person is a director of the body corporate at that time; or\
	(c)	in the case of a trust in which the trustee, or one or more of the trustees, is an individual\'97the individual is a trustee of the trust at that time; or\
	(d)	in the case of a trust in which the trustee, or one or more of the trustees, is a body corporate\'97the person is a director of the body corporate at that time; or\
	(e)	in the case of an unincorporated association\'97the person is a member of the governing body of the unincorporated association at that time.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb280\partightenfactor0

