\f1\b\fs24 \cf0 87  Rules\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs22 \cf0 	(1)	The Minister may, by legislative instrument, make rules prescribing matters:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	required or permitted by this Act to be prescribed by the rules; or\
	(b)	necessary or convenient to be prescribed for carrying out or giving effect to this Act.\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(2)	To avoid doubt, the
\f2\i  
\f0\i0 rules may not do the following:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	create an offence or civil penalty;\
	(b)	provide powers of:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	arrest or detention; or\
	(ii)	entry, search or seizure;\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(c)	impose a tax;\
	(d)	set an amount to be appropriated from the Consolidated Revenue Fund under an appropriation in this Act;\
	(e)	directly amend the text of this Act.\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(3)	Before making or amending the rules, the Minister must:\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(a)	cause to be published on the Department\'92s website a notice:\
\pard\tqr\tx1985\pardeftab720\li2098\fi-2098\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(i)	setting out the draft rules or amendments; and\
	(ii)	inviting persons to make submissions to the Minister about the draft rules or amendments within the period specified in the notice; and\
\pard\tqr\tx1531\pardeftab720\li1644\fi-1644\ri1933\sb40\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(b)	consider any submissions received within the period mentioned in subparagraph\'a0(a)(ii).\
\pard\tqr\tx1021\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb180\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	(4)	The period specified in the notice must not be shorter than 28 days.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1134\fi-1134\ri1933\sb280\partightenfactor0

